net.sf.mmm.client.ui.base.widget.complex

Interface ItemContainer<ITEM,SELF extends ItemContainer<ITEM,SELF>>

  • Type Parameters:
    ITEM - is the generic type of the contained item.
    SELF - is the generic type of this container itself.
    All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeReadSelected, AttributeReadSelectionMode, AttributeReadValue<ITEM>, AttributeWriteSelected, AttributeWriteSelectionMode
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    NodeContainer<NODE,SELF>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractItemContainer, AbstractNodeContainer, ItemContainerGwt

    public interface ItemContainer<ITEM,SELF extends ItemContainer<ITEM,SELF>>
extends AttributeWriteSelected, AttributeWriteSelectionMode, AttributeReadValue<ITEM>
    This is the interface for a container for an <ITEM> of a data set widget. It can be implemented toolkit specific implementation that contains the raw widget to render the item.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
